Ingame keys
-----------

1    Cycle controls for Shinobi
2    Cycle controls for the dark forces
M    Music on/off
P    Pause on/off
+    Increase game speed
-    Decrease game speed
Esc  Quit


Controls
--------

Shinobi and the Karate Gang:

Without button                      With button

B   8  1  2   F   1 Block           B   8  1  2   F   1 Jump kick
A    \ | /    O   2 Punch           A    \ | /    O   2 Kick to head
C     \|/     R   3 Move Forward    C     \|/     R   3 Kick to stomach
K 7 --- --- 3 W   4 -               K 7 ---*--- 3 W   4 -
W     /|\     A   5 Get down        W     /|\     A   5 Kick to knee
A    / | \    R   6 -               A    / | \    R   6 Roundkick to head
R   6  5  4   D   7 Move Backward   R   6  5  4   D   7 Volt
D                 8 Turn around     D                 8 Roundpunch to head



The stick man:

Without button                      With button

B   8  1  2   F   1 Block           B   8  1  2   F   1 Jump kick
A    \ | /    O   2 Stick poke      A    \ | /    O   2 Kick to head
C     \|/     R   3 Move Forward    C     \|/     R   3 Kick to stomach
K 7 --- --- 3 W   4 -               K 7 ---*--- 3 W   4 -
W     /|\     A   5 Get down        W     /|\     A   5 Kick to feet
A    / | \    R   6 -               A    / | \    R   6 Roundkick to head
R   6  5  4   D   7 Move Backward   R   6  5  4   D   7 Another Stick poke
D                 8 Turn around     D                 8 -


Karbas:

Without button                      With button

B   8  1  2   F   1 Block           B   8  1  2   F   1 Crunch punch
A    \ | /    O   2 Punch           A    \ | /    O   2 -
C     \|/     R   3 Move Forward    C     \|/     R   3 Destruction punch
K 7 --- --- 3 W   4 -               K 7 ---*--- 3 W   4 Slam
W     /|\     A   5 -               W     /|\     A   5 Crouch punch
A    / | \    R   6 -               A    / | \    R   6 -
R   6  5  4   D   7 Move Backward   R   6  5  4   D   7 Roundpunch to head
D                 8 Turn around     D                 8 Flail



Throw-ninja:

Without button                      With button

B   8  1  2   F   1 Block           B   8  1  2   F   1 Jump kick
A    \ | /    O   2 Punch           A    \ | /    O   2 Kick to head
C     \|/     R   3 Move Forward    C     \|/     R   3 Kick to stomach
K 7 --- --- 3 W   4 -               K 7 ---*--- 3 W   4 Throw a star
W     /|\     A   5 Get down        W     /|\     A   5 Kick to knee
A    / | \    R   6 Grab'n'punch    A    / | \    R   6 Roundkick to head
R   6  5  4   D   7 Move Backward   R   6  5  4   D   7 Volt
D                 8 Turn around     D                 8 Roundpunch to head

+ Some C00l special moves! Check 'em out!

Dragon:

Without button                      With button

B   8  1  2   F   1 Block           B   8  1  2   F   1 Jump kick
A    \ | /    O   2 Punch           A    \ | /    O   2 Kick to head
C     \|/     R   3 Move Forward    C     \|/     R   3 Kick to stomach
K 7 --- --- 3 W   4 -               K 7 ---*--- 3 W   4 DUUUUUING!
W     /|\     A   5 Get down        W     /|\     A   5 Kick to feet
A    / | \    R   6 -               A    / | \    R   6 Roundkick to head
R   6  5  4   D   7 Move Backward   R   6  5  4   D   7 Entity sword swing
D                 8 Turn around     D                 8 Chop some meat

We don't know the exact names of the moves in english, so you better just
try them.


